latestPosts.caption:
“From childhood laughs to movie nights—some friendships never change 🫶✨ 

“Watching Lilo & Stitch with my +1 just reminded me why she’s my forever 🐶💫

“Good food, great movie, and the best company. What more do you need? 🥹💙

“You, me, and Stitch made the perfect trio last night 🐾💫

“Friendship like Lilo & Stitch’s is rare—chaotic, cute, and completely unbreakable 🐾💙

“Some bonds are stitched into your soul. 

“We laughed, we cried, we hugged it out—Disney really knows how to hit the heart 🎥🫂

“When your bestie is your +1 for everything, including Disney premieres 🥰🍿

“Last night was all about good vibes and even better memories with my bestie 💫
